Specified oil Grade: API service GL- 4 or GL- 5 Viscosity: SAE 75W- 90 (All season) or SAE 80W- 90 (Above 10 °C (50 °F)) Capacity: 2.0 L (2.1 US qt, 1.8 Imp qt)  


3. Wipe the plug clean and apply sealant to the plug threads before installing.  


Tightening torque A: 25- 39 N·m (2.5- 4.0 kgf·m, 19- 28 ft·lbf)